<< Installing js project>>
1. Install node.js
  // npm package manager was installed automatically
      * to control dependencies,
      * to create libraries
2. install packages:
2.1. Global installation:
  $ nmp install -g eslint babel
  Running:
  $ eslint main.js
  $ babel-node main.js
